case.title: Free this weekend? - 26 (London)
case.text: Hey so am free this weekend and was wondering if any guy would like to meet up for a drink and good chat . Lets talk about things in general . Please I would prefer a single guy matured and can hold up a good decent conversation age race unimportant . Is not a date ! Is only a friendly meet up . Am a black lady single and free! Please email your pics and lets get started!
